1. scala下载慢

http://downloads.typesafe.com/scala/2.12.12/scala-2.12.12.tgz


2. pyspark 使用python3

只需要在bin/pyspark中增加

export PYSPARK_PYTHON=python3


修改spark-env.sh文件，在末尾添加export PYSPARK_PYTHON=/usr/bin/python3



sysctl -a |grep hung_task_timeout_secs

sysctl -w vm.dirty_ratio=10

sysctl -w vm.dirty_background_ratio=5

sysctl -w kernel.hung_task_timeout_secs=0

sysctl -p

Bad owner or permissions on /root/.ssh/confi
